</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Soweto_Cooling_Towers.JPG" class="image" title="Another example of painted cooling towers on the Orlando Power Station in Soweto, South Africa."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/08/Soweto_Cooling_Towers.JPG/180px-Soweto_Cooling_Towers.JPG" width="180" height="135" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
